This was a topic he had seen brought up before, time and time again, when he had been alive... nothing new.<br>
Still, you took entertainment where you could when you were nothing but a silent wraith. Smiling slightly, Inthul continued to follow the bickering voices back and forth, his cloudy red eyes studying the faces of those he had once known. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Baron Inthul L`akai`zhar</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
