Nay! Lady Genashai . The husband you say abused you so badly after so many years of your devotion to him, tells a different story. His tears wet my shoulder day after day in his grief and longing for you.Yet your heart was cold to him and upon your learning of his dependance on my support did you not decide to take that which was mine?  Namely the said Wood Elf so recently my lover. You can not deny you knew he was mine, for did you not ask me if I had taken your past Lord to my bed?  I did say  it was not so, for at the time this was true indeed. Did I not tell you that I loved the Wood Elf with a burning passion that you had seen for your own eyes many times. Yet you pursued him.<br>
Now knowing  where my love was when he was not at my side  I wonder.....  did you not feel any pangs of regret at the harm and the pain you were causing me...who had tried to be friend to you?<br>
You may wish my lover's heart for the moment, but know this  thing, Lady. He who is untrue to one woman will be untrue to another. He will try to return to me, of that I have no doubt.<br>
While your Lord's tears have dried on my cloak, his need  for me has grown and I admit I am warmed in my own grief with the love he now bears me, and although I did not seek to have this happen, when grief meets grief, comfort may turn to love.<br>
Know one thing more. The Wood Elf denies any love for you other then what is in your own head and states that he still loves me. Why only one day past,  he said we would would marry and I would wear his name. I know not what to believe. I wish to accept his word that there is nothing between the two of you but will not take him back to my bed if the words he whispers in both our ears are mere falsehoods.<br>
While I ponder these things, I shall continue to care and cherish that which you have lost, for this Knight's devotion to me is open and clear and full of promise and hope for the future. I will not lie to him or he to me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=genashai>Genashai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 89<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/9/03 1:35 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Real Love</span><hr size=1> Deleted. my apologies to the population for making something private, public. <br>
